{"$content":[{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_00_000","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Come on, everybody gets one storybook.","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_008","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_00_001","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Hehe, after you're finished, don't forget to lend it to someone else.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_00_002","SpeakerName":"Grumbling Orphan","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3349c3","IconName":"t3349c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Thank you, High Priest...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_01_000","SpeakerName":"Grumbling Orphan","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3349c3","IconName":"t3349c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Tsk...another book about the Snake God~","sfxName":"human_male_teen_03","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_01_001","SpeakerName":"Fed Up Orhapn","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3350c3","IconName":"t3350c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"This sucks. I'm sick of this crap. So boring! I'd rather have some nice clothes and a doll~","sfxName":"human_female_kid_03","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_01_002","SpeakerName":"Grumbling Orphan","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3349c3","IconName":"t3349c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Devious is going to tell us the same old story again. We'd better go play somewhere else!","sfxName":"human_male_teen_09","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_01_003","SpeakerName":"Joshua","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3353c3","IconName":"h3353c3_4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"......","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_02_000","SpeakerName":"Headmaster","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3193c3","IconName":"t3193c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Thank you, High Priest, for giving the children so many books.","sfxName":"human_female_young_01","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_02_001","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"... *sigh*... I wanted to bring some clothes and toys for the children,  but the donations to the Shrine are not what they used to be...","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_002_ver1","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_02_002","SpeakerName":"Headmaster","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3193c3","IconName":"t3193c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Indeed...to be honest, these past few years the nobles have rarely offered subsidies to the orphanage.","sfxName":"human_female_young_10","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_02_003","SpeakerName":"Headmaster","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3193c3","IconName":"t3193c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"The orphanage on the east side may even have to close its doors...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_03_000","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_sorrow","IconLocate":2,"Text":"... *sigh*... The aristocrats, it doesn't matter who dies, all they care about is the struggle for the throne. 
It's no surprise they don't attend to other matters.","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_030","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_03_001","SpeakerName":"Headmaster","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3193c3","IconName":"t3193c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I hope these conflicts come to an end soon...","sfxName":"human_female_young_01","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_04_000","SpeakerName":"Young Cleric","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3158c2","IconName":"t3158c2_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"High Priest, it is almost time to hold the evening prayer. We ought to be getting back to the Shrine. ","sfxName":"human_female_young_royal_01","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_05_000","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"When I am free I will bring some things back with me. Please, take care of the children.","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_001","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_06_000","SpeakerName":"Young Cleric","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3158c2","IconName":"t3158c2_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"If the High Priest really wants to help the orphans, there must be an easier way...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_06_001","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You...what do you mean?","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_003","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_06_002","SpeakerName":"Young Cleric","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3158c2","IconName":"t3158c2_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"High Priest, you know as well as I do that many of the nobles would love the support of the Shrine...","sfxName":"human_female_middle_royal_03","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_07_000","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Enough! The struggle for the throne is a display of God's will, an expression of the natural order! 

If we interfere for our own benefit, the Snake God will never forgive us!","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_021","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_07_001","SpeakerName":"Young Cleric","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3158c2","IconName":"t3158c2_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Who is more knowledgable about the will of the Snake God and Goddess than you──","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_07_002","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Enough! Let's go!","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_005","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_08_000","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_surprise","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You...!","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_003","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_09_000","SpeakerName":"Andrew","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3302c4","IconName":"t3302c4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Andrew Giuliano Gomez, of the royal family. We've met before, High Priest.","sfxName":"human_male_middle_soldier_01_ver1","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_10_000","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You! It was you──","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_026","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_10_001","SpeakerName":"Andrew","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3302c4","IconName":"t3302c4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Please, High Priest, don't misunderstand me. I have been trying to meet with you for some time now.","sfxName":"human_male_middle_soldier_03","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_10_002","SpeakerName":"Andrew","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3302c4","IconName":"t3302c4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I just want to sit down and talk with you...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_10_003","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"So you've been getting close with and using my clerics!","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_014","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_10_004","SpeakerName":"Young Cleric","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3158c2","IconName":"t3158c2_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"High Priest, please hear Mr. Gomez out!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_10_005","SpeakerName":"Joshua","SpeakerAssetName":"","IconName":"0_no_face","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Help!!!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_11_000","SpeakerName":"Andrew","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3302c4","IconName":"t3302c4_surprise","IconLocate":2,"Text":"It's a child! ","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_12_000","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_surprise","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Joshua!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_13_000","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Joshua, why are you trying to sneak into the Shrine again?","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_014","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_13_001","SpeakerName":"Joshua","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3353c3","IconName":"h3353c3_4_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Because, I-I...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_14_000","SpeakerName":"Joshua","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3353c3","IconName":"h3353c3_4_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I don't want to stay in the orphanage any longer! I'm not an orphan!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_14_001","SpeakerName":"Andrew","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3302c4","IconName":"t3302c4_surprise","IconLocate":2,"Text":"High Priest, this is...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_15_000","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Six months ago, this child was abandoned in the Shrine by his parents...","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_030","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_15_001","SpeakerName":"Joshua","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3353c3","IconName":"h3353c3_4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I was not abandoned! I j-j-just got lost!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_15_002","SpeakerName":"Joshua","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3353c3","IconName":"h3353c3_4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Maybe my mom is still in the Shrine waiting for me...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_15_003","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Joshua, I understand how you feel...but if you keep running away without telling anyone, we'll all be worried about you.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_15_004","SpeakerName":"Joshua","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3353c3","IconName":"h3353c3_4_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I...but I...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_15_005","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Okay, why don't you come back to the Shrine with me tonight? I'll take you back tomorrow.","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_002_ver1","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_15_006","SpeakerName":"Andrew","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3302c4","IconName":"t3302c4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Let me take you and the child back. I wouldn't want you to run into more monsters.","sfxName":"human_male_middle_soldier_01_ver1","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_15_007","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"...Fine. Thank you for your kindness.","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_001","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_16_000","SpeakerName":"Young Cleric","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3158c2","IconName":"t3158c2_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"High Priest, it's an infant. She's a snake demihuman...inside there's a note that says the family is unable to raise the child.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_16_001","SpeakerName":"Young Cleric","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3158c2","IconName":"t3158c2_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"They hope the Snake God will care for her...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_16_002","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_sorrow","IconLocate":2,"Text":"...*sigh*...poor child. This is already the third this month...","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_028","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_17_000","SpeakerName":"Joshua","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3353c3","IconName":"h3353c3_4_surprise","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Do her father and mother not want her...?","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_18_000","SpeakerName":"Andrew","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3302c4","IconName":"t3302c4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Does this happen often?","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_18_001","SpeakerName":"Andrew","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3302c4","IconName":"t3302c4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I mean...children being abandoned at the entrance of the Shrine...?","sfxName":"human_male_middle_soldier_03","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_18_002","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Sir, it's certainly more than you can even imagine.","sfxName":"t0153sx_story_030","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_19_000","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Tomorrow I will do as I always do and send this child to the orphanage.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_19_001","SpeakerName":"Devious","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t0153","IconName":"t0153s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Thank you for seeing us home.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_t0153_001_dialog_english##_20_000","SpeakerName":"Andrew","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/t3302c4","IconName":"t3302c4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"......","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0}]}
